Jayde is lost in her own vehement ramblings when her computer picks 
up a spark signature.  Looking down, she sees Spike below.  
Recognizing him as one of the group that was attacking Megatron's 
base earlier, and remembering the unofficial alliance the Rogues have 
with Megatron's forces, she takes this as an opportunity to vent 
frustration.

As her cloaking device deactivates for an attack, Jayde's sleek 
vehicle form becomes visible and the sound of her engine can now be 
heard plainly - as can the shriek of her ionic blaster as she strafes 
the Tripredacus warrior.
